個whatsapp 去另一個google drive 係咪應該就唔驚刪左人地個whatsap data<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔同acc就唔怕overwrite"},{"pid":"cf1e9836bbb5296e88fead09568f07422d30b6ea","tid":119004,"uid":66506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:27:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一係你就搵部Android機load左你個History落去，之後再用Backuptrans過落iPhone到<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係就無啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nLoad history 之前backup 人地個whatsapp 去另一個google drive 係咪應該就唔驚刪左人地個whatsap data<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔同<span style=\"color: red;\">google</span> acc就唔怕overwrite</blockquote>"},{"pid":"47ae42278b802c51ee76c24574afc408aa1c8722","tid":119004,"uid":71365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:28:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一係你就搵部Android機load左你個History落去，之後再用Backuptrans過落iPhone到<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係就無啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我部舊機會拎去整，如果我唔restore係iPhone 重新用，舊機整番好會唔會restore 唔到google drive data , google drive backup 會唔會因為我用iPhone whatsapp 而無左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be13ebd161b17cd5d9c334b70e8e9b8a2b26ae29","tid":119004,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T01:35:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一係你就搵部Android機load左你個History落去，之後再用Backuptrans過落iPhone到<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係就無啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我部舊機會拎去整，如果我唔restore係iPhone 重新用，舊機整番好會唔會restore 唔到google drive data , google drive backup 會唔會因為我用iPhone whatsapp 而無左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAn機save係Google，iPhone save係iCloud<br />\nGoogle同iCloud唔可以直接過到資料俾大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你整你部An舊機，同iPhone係無關係<br />\n整好左部機，自不然可以access到去你個Google Drive到，拎到啲data<br />\n咁先可以再用Backuptrans過落去iPhone"},{"pid":"99d442660e41da277c522506c1ba364b72f54e90","tid":119004,"uid":44440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T01:41:54.000Z","msg":"有個exe可以幫到你喎 不過要比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申自己都係咁轉"},{"pid":"ac650f95fcef3980940beef5ccc21cc550754171","tid":119004,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T01:57:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個exe可以幫到你喎 不過要比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申自己都係咁轉</blockquote><br />\nBackuptrans呀嘛，上面講左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55b6086036add5f938993650371f114f47f07b2","tid":119004,"uid":22948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T03:04:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一係你就搵部Android機load左你個History落去，之後再用Backuptrans過落iPhone到<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係就無啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正解"}]}